      "status": "translated",
      "translation": "### 图表：mermaid 和 excalidraw fence 会被渲染成图片"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "make-pdf-0132-paragraph",
      "source_hash": "a5e39bb268209e2960de3682b5e704ab1e294d6e8f676ee44d37d47263ddd461",
      "status": "translated",
      "translation": "Markdown 中位于第 0 列的 ` ```mermaid ` 或 ` ```excalidraw ` fence 会渲染为清晰的矢量图，并且完全离线（vendored bundle，无 CDN）。缩进的 fence（位于列表内部）会按设计保留为普通代码块。损坏的 fence 会生成可见的红色诊断块，显示解析错误，绝不会静默输出原始代码。"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "make-pdf-0133-paragraph",
      "source_hash": "44c8b19be14b035b7ab79e0374687da1a613e96258359cf58ea937bdbf2d3810",
      "status": "translated",
      "translation": "Fence info-string 选项："
    },
    {
      "block_id": "make-pdf-0134-code-block",
      "source_hash": "19723e64df1d3a26224b79adf27e75846ece0344ec28040d82799bb2129d441b",
      "status": "translated",
      "translation": "```\n```mermaid title=\"Auth flow\"        ← 图注 + aria-label"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "make-pdf-0135-code-block",
      "source_hash": "d8961b403bcc47759baa413dff965bd398c4924546f731a32296c79c704b2899",
      "status": "translated",
      "translation": "```mermaid render=false             ← 保留为代码块（当前行为）\n```mermaid page=landscape           ← 强制把这个图表放到横向页面"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "make-pdf-0136-code-block",
      "source_hash": "2aab13d282e02c5dc0729781bc660b2e395c50266220976e5577d6273f15aef7",
      "status": "translated",
      "translation": "```mermaid page=portrait            ← 否决自动横向页面\n```"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "make-pdf-0137-paragraph",
      "source_hash": "3ea57e1a21fc73e0b6e75e87b175ac200d443896044cc7768be2c4e9fc3aa4f2",
      "status": "translated",
      "translation": "` ```excalidraw ` fence 包含一个完整的 `.excalidraw` 场景文件（excalidraw.com 保存的格式）。从英文描述创作新图表是 `/diagram` 的职责，它会输出一个可编辑三件套（source、`.excalidraw`、SVG/PNG），并与本 skill 配合：把 `.mmd` 源嵌入 Markdown，而不是嵌入 PNG。"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "make-pdf-0138-heading",
      "source_hash": "40209662313205bd042129907c0e026cf209059018f6fc6e4200b214c0a5aad0",
      "status": "translated",
      "translation": "### 图片：正确缩放，绝不截断"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "make-pdf-0139-paragraph",
      "source_hash": "79680e0044d9dcaa56b10fff53253f7f090b1efeeccfbb8a60a6fb65b5bb45ec",
      "status": "translated",
      "translation": "本地图片会自动内联（相对路径按 Markdown 文件解析）。每张图片都会限制在内容框内，永远不会截断。超大照片会降采样到打印分辨率（300dpi），因此 payload 保持较小，同时没有可见质量损失。"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "make-pdf-0140-paragraph",
      "source_hash": "446cf1d1c866abf6296e83dfb87ad7a50f4f988c3ee8e3e0335e27904e0d8aca",
      "status": "translated",
      "translation": "远程（http/https）图片默认会被**阻止，并显示可见占位符**，这是离线姿态；传入 `--allow-network` 才会抓取。解析到 Markdown 目录之外的图片（即使通过 symlink）仍会内联，但会明确警告；`--strict` 会把它变成致命错误。超过 64MB 的文件或非普通文件（fifo、device）会降级为占位符，而不是卡住运行。"
    }
  ]
